  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="faq">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>How do I book a movie or show ticket?</h3>
        <p>Booking a ticket is simple! Browse through the available options, select your preferred time slot, seat, and
          payment method, and confirm your booking. You’ll receive an e-ticket via email immediately.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>What payment methods do you accept?</h3>
        <p>We accept all major credit and debit cards, as well as PayPal, Apple Pay, and Google Wallet for quick and
          secure transactions.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>How do I cancel or modify my booking?</h3>
        <p>You can cancel or modify your booking up to 2 hours before the showtime. To do so, simply log into your
          Moviesta account, go to 'My Bookings,' and select the ticket you wish to modify or cancel. Additional charges
          may apply.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>Can I request a refund?</h3>
        <p>Refunds are available for cancellations made within the allowed timeframe. For more details, refer to our <a
            href="#">Refund Policy</a>.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>Do you offer discounts for bulk bookings?</h3>
        <p>Yes, we offer special discounts for bulk or group bookings. Contact our support team at
          <strong>sales@Moviesta.com</strong> for more information on bulk offers and corporate packages.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

